{"tid":1375011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：高度表揚警務人員盡忠職守","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T22:59:46.000Z","uid":20933,"like":13,"dislike":1298,"uniUserReply":177,"replies":[{"pid":"6618419c16803cce3ef03c29a9be51ece73a5816","tid":1375011,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日前因向公眾道歉，而引起多個警察協會不滿的政務司司長張建宗發表網誌。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗撰文，記述月中與幾名學生到天文台參觀，令他聯想到天氣縱然陰晴不定，只要沉著應對再大風雨過後總會有晴天。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗周五就警方在元朗襲擊事件中的處理手法向公眾道歉，引起多個警察協會不滿，政務司司長辦公室指，張建宗絕對支持及衷心感謝警隊的執法工作，亦高度表揚警務人員在困難期間承受重大壓力仍然盡忠職守，致力維持社會治安，會盡快安排與相關警務人員協會會面，澄清誤會及加强溝通。"},{"pid":"c9264acae71ab689c2ea8c8e13ce3b992e71da71","tid":1375011,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=357018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357018&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=449af9eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357018&h=e955365f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=357018</a>"},{"pid":"1695bea8aa17d8a81101099dbf42896a02e37f19","tid":1375011,"uid":74622,"like":449,"dislike":0,"score":449,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"牆頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1493245316906a6ed8aaa54a60b24dcdeeb08f32","tid":1375011,"uid":79117,"like":469,"dislike":2,"score":467,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"証明香港已經係軍政府，解放軍來了我帶來。同志，這邊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5cd5d20a32bc6221